sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(via EPP/Gateway)
    participant Sidecar as llm-d-routing-sidecar<br/>:8000/TCP HTTPS
    participant Allowlist as AllowlistValidator<br/>(in-process)
    participant Prefiller as Remote vLLM Prefiller<br/>{host}:{port}
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>localhost:8001/TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>x-prefiller-host-port: {host}:{port}<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Sidecar->>Allowlist: Validate prefiller host<br/>(if SSRF protection enabled)
    Allowlist-->>Sidecar: Allowed / 403 Forbidden

    Sidecar->>Prefiller: Forward request + kv_transfer_params<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (optional TLS)
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Prefill response (buffered)<br/>KV-cache transfer metadata

    Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward original request +<br/>kv_transfer_params from prefill<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (optional TLS)
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Decode response (streamed)

    Sidecar-->>Client: Final response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Pass-through (No Prefill Header)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Transparent proxy<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (optional TLS)
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Response
    Sidecar-->>Client: Proxied response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Sidecar,K8sAPI: Flow 3: SSRF Allowlist Update (Background)

    Sidecar->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool CR<br/>HTTPS/TLS, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Sidecar: InferencePool events<br/>(label selectors)
    Sidecar->>K8sAPI: Watch Pods matching selectors<br/>HTTPS/TLS, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Sidecar: Pod events<br/>(IPs, names)
    Note over Allowlist: Rebuild allowlist<br/>atomically on<br/>pod add/update/delete<br/>(30s resync)
